Type: Package
Package: godley
Title: Stock-Flow-Consistent Model Simulator
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Iwo", "Augustynski", , "iwo.a@int.pl", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Julian", "Kacprzak", role = "aut"),
    person("Michal", "Gamrot", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Define, simulate and validate SFC models. The accounting
    structure of SFC models are described in Godley and Lavoie (2007,
    ISBN:978-1-137-08599-3). The algorithms implemented to solve the
    models are described in Kinsella and O'Shea (2010)
    <doi:10.2139/ssrn.1729205> and Peressini and Sullivan (1988,
    ISBN:0-387-96614-5) and Joao Macalos.
License: GPL (>= 3)
